# West Bengal Information Portal

A modern, responsive and user-friendly information portal for the Government of West Bengal.

## Features

- Government Departments
- Government Jobs
- Government Schemes
- Education
- Latest News
- Weather
- All 23 Districts
- Search
- Dark Mode
- Emergency Numbers
- Mobile Responsive
- SEO Ready
- AdSense Ready

